downloadTitle: Variations planning worksheet for SharePoint Server 2013 and SharePoint Online
downloadDescription: Use this worksheet to capture necessary details about source sites and target sites when you plan variations for sites in SharePoint Server 2013.
detailsSection: Use this worksheet to capture necessary details about source sites and target sites when you plan variations for sites in SharePoint Server 2013.
systemRequirementsSection: Microsoft Excel 2007, Microsoft Excel 2010, Microsoft Excel 2013
installInstructionSection:
1. Click the Download button in the upper right corner of this page to start the download.
  2. Click Save or Save this program to disk.
  3. Find the file on your hard disk and double-click it to open it.
